             - Purpose: Represents a table in MySQL (users table).
üß© Step 4 ‚Äî Repository Layer
             - Purpose: Provides CRUD operations (save, findAll, findById, delete) without writing SQL.
üß© Step 5 ‚Äî Service Layer
             - Purpose: Business logic layer.
üß© Step 6 ‚Äî PDF Generation Class (Helper)
             - Purpose: Converts list of users into a PDF file. /  Returns byte[] ‚Üí can be sent as HTTP response./ Uses iText to create title, table, fonts, and rows.
üß© Step 7 ‚Äî Controller Layer            
            - Purpose: endpoint: Saves user to database.   /  Fetches all users and generates PDF for download.











